{"type":"message","id":"38d3a5fb","parentId":"1befea33","timestamp":"2026-04-10T13:57:30.111Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Still getting the same error. The proxy service appears to be down or has a deployment issue. I should inform the user about this and suggest alternatives.\n\nThe Midjourney service via the proxy is unavailable. I should let the user know and maybe suggest trying again later or using Flux as an alternative (though Flux doesn't do Midjourney style).","thinkingSignature":"0b076246e8536c4f5cf1b116f18811c3b86ffc523437dc9e2431ab9df56da00a"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉 😔 **Midjourney API 服务目前不可用**（部署未找到错误）。\n\n**替代方案**：\n1. **稍后再试** - 可能是 Vercel 冷启动问题\n2. **使用 Flux 图像** - ¥0.01，虽然不是真正的 MJ 风格，但可以尝试\"印象派\"提示词\n\n要不要我先用 Flux 试一个印象派风格的曼哈顿？或者等会儿再试 MJ？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minim","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2553,"output":165,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":18775,"totalTokens":21493,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775829442774,"responseId":"062834c3f2072697c0e7538089e2be12"}}
